咗荷包着想，試過補時換佢出嚟踢1分鐘都要做足&hellip;&hellip;皇馬咁樣做，聽落好揠苗助長喎。</blockquote><br />\n應該係唔出場就要出部份週薪<br />\n利申玩開fm"},{"pid":"9aa025edf92aea0a84563ca5b84d01a42e4a3455","tid":264773,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>halilovic勁過佢<br />\n<br />\n但養和b同拉豬福特吊打</blockquote><br />\n系"},{"pid":"90bdb1c9ee6a181a91c15688b37a5108d1134c32","tid":264773,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"打fifa都唔用佢啦 fifa入邊佢得4x體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}